Package com.jpl.nasa.scihound

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminInformation
    Class that holds the Admin-set information.
    AggregatedPointInformation
    Collected Points Information: Point's location data, photo file path, DateTime, etc.
    CameraIntent
    Class that handles the access of the Camera.
    CheckPermission
    A static class that will be used throughout the application to check if the application has the necessary permissions.
    FileCreation
    Class to create CSV files or files for photos.
    LoadProjectsFromTemplateFile
    Class that parses the project_template file in the ../res/raw/ directory.
    MainActivity
    The Login activity that prompts the user for an email as well as the verification password that was assigned in AdminInformation.
    PointsListAdapter
    List Adapter for the ListView that will hold all of the points on the interface for Project Interface.
    ProjectChoosingInterface
    The Project choosing interface class.
    ProjectInterface
    The specific project interface that the user wants to collect the points of.
    ProjectListAdapter
    List Adapter for the project choosing interface ListView.
    ProjectToPoints
    Holds the project with the collected points for that project.
    ProjectTypes
    Class that holds the different types of projects, project links, and land cover classes.
    SendPointsInEmail
    The class that handles the email intent by collecting all of the point information and then starting the intent.
    UserInformation
    Class that holds the user's email information, this is collected on the login page.
    VisualizePoints
    The class allows the user to visualize the points that they have collect.
